        {
            "title": "東京4月CPI小幅上升,核心通膨進一步跌破日本央行目標",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/8gTqaFMTTuyzDgP1AaS41Q--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXNPEC501G5_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- 東京4月消費者物價指數通膨小幅上升,而核心通膨則進一步跌破<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"日本央行\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:日本央行;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/日本央行\">日本央行</a>的年度目標,因持續的政府補貼有助於抵消伊朗戰爭導致的能源價格衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">政府週五公布的數據顯示,整體CPI在4月上升1.5%,3月為1.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東京核心CPI(不包括波動較大的新鮮食品價格)在4月上升1.5%,3月為1.7%。該數據低於1.8%的預期,進一步跌破日本央行2%的年度目標,也創下四年來最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">同時排除新鮮食品和能源價格的核心讀數在4月降至1.9%,3月為2.3%,創下14個月低點。該數據被日本央行密切關注,作為衡量潛在通膨的指標。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c8f5610c-57e0-3952-85be-994eeaf508e4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通膨數據走軟,是因為政府對公用事業(特別是天然氣和電力)的補貼仍在實施,抵消了因伊朗戰爭導致供應中斷而推高天然氣價格的影響。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">公共和私人交通成本增長緩慢,因東京也開始釋放戰略石油儲備以穩定本地供應。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">東京通膨通常被視為全國CPI的先行指標,週五的數據尚未完全反映伊朗戰爭和高能源價格的全面影響。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">但該數據公布之際,日本央行剛在數日前維持利率不變,但大幅上調了2026年的通膨預測,同時警告稱面對日益頑固的通膨,將進一步加息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">日本央行也下調了經濟增長預測,預期伊朗戰爭將帶來阻力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%B1%E4%BA%AC4%E6%9C%88cpi%E5%B0%8F%E5%B9%85%E4%B8%8A%E5%8D%87-%E6%A0%B8%E5%BF%83%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E9%80%B2-%E6%AD%A5%E8%B7%8C%E7%A0%B4%E6%97%A5%E6%9C%AC%E5%A4%AE%E8%A1%8C%E7%9B%AE%E6%A8%99-004400353.html",
